    "bfc_repair_section_9mhfab": {
      "type": "bfc-repair-section",
      "custom_css": [],
      "name": "BFC Repair (Offline)",
      "settings": {
        "turnaround_show": true,
        "turnaround_label": "Current Turnaround:",
        "turnaround_text": "8 to 12 Weeks",
        "turnaround_show_dot": true,
        "turnaround_style": "accent",
        "hero_headline": "<p>Expert repair for cameras worth keeping</p>",
        "hero_tagline": "<p>In-house technicians. Transparent quotes. No work starts until you approve. Mail-in or drop off at 855 Grand St, Brooklyn.</p>",
        "url_44r2z7TSjcGHkDEt-1": "shopify://pages/film-camera-repairs-1",
        "text_OGVmSdENOpRpSm1q-1": "<p>Start Repair</p>",
        "text_b1ethHm88r6HXMAG-1": "<h4><strong>Step 1: Start your Repair</strong></h4>",
        "text_zK5b4fQevS7bQERJ-1": "<p>Complete our online form and provide as much information and photos, if available.</p>",
        "text_0si98RFp5joWJ1B8-1": "<h4><strong>Step 2: get Your Camera to us</strong></h4>",
        "text_3lXcPM5OEDXNzDbL-1": "<p>Pack your camera securely and ship it to our Brooklyn HQ with one of our prepaid shipping labels. Cameras can also be dropped off in person during normal business hours.</p>",
        "text_uoM6sBLNDaHyMRgg-1": "<h4><strong>Step 3 : Technical Assessment</strong></h4>",
        "text_RPTUdA1bfP1WKHbf-1": "<p>Our technicians will perform a comprehensive diagnostic of your camera.</p>",
        "text_bWF9lADjf58RmD6y-1": "<h4><strong>Step 4: Receive Your Repair Quote</strong></h4>",
        "text_IdTYOB7FDYASZcxP-1": "<p>We'll contact you with a detailed breakdown of what needs to be repaired and the associated costs. Once approved, the initial $50 inspection fee is applied toward the cost of your repair.</p>",
        "text_HrsD7nsiZ51a7coM-1": "<h4><strong>Step 5: Expert Repair Work</strong></h4>",
        "text_T4nRNJtWXNje3fMK-1": "<p>Once you approve our quote we will begin the repair process using quality parts and factory approved techniques.</p>",
        "text_kxIcPYlQOEUWoLHz-1": "<h4><strong>Step 6: Quality Testing & Return</strong></h4>",
        "text_dAmEcKiEXHxfrQ9v-1": "<p>Once completed your camera goes thorough our testing process to ensure everything functions exactly as it should.</p>",
        "text_nsHGXN0PI3XSWcih-1": "<p>We are actively expanding our repair menu. If you don't see your camera listed in our menu you can still request a quote by selecting \"unlisted.\"</p>",
        "text_e3IgUtmnx0JCNiDZ-1": "<h3>Canon AE-1 Program</h3>",
        "text_nSvnmtcQ01027Xj7-1": "<p>One of our most popular services we can perform everything on a Canon AE-1 Program.</p>",
        "text_0GXley78XRccVff6-1": "<h3>K1000</h3>",
        "text_4V3mnOu74Winkojf-1": "<p>Another popular service, we are setup to handle every issue with the K1000</p>",
        "text_P6UogtMNA3NTe4iU-1": "<h3>Hasselblad 500 Series</h3>",
        "text_xj27KEgUVzPLcNGZ-1": "<p>Our dedicated Hasselblad tech can perform full CLA on any 500 series body.</p>",
        "text_huNJv1FaXJPXBXne-1": "<h3>Contax T</h3>",
        "text_fpHh06dolmevW9rt-1": "<p>Specializing in Contax for years, our technicians can do throuoguh repairs on Contaxt T</p>",
        "text_pXhOtTQSfrgaTNZM-1": "<h3>Contax G2</h3>",
        "text_wTI1WAcR4j4D1JgN-1": "<p>Calibration, full CLAs, repairs, and more—if it’s acting up, just bring it in!</p>",
        "text_zj5YYBoqEAS4JhTb-1": "<h3>Other Cameras</h3>",
        "text_AnBPyLkv0Y3ci8Wo-1": "<p>We also CLA - Contax T, TVS, T2's, Canonet's, canon P's. Don't see your camera? Email us, we do more!</p>",
        "text_f4piqP05EzMfEZYr-1": "<h3>Light Seals</h3>",
        "text_OanafuXt1OjroSZu-1": "<p>We can replace the foam on all cameras</p>",
        "text_OXdu84QbSBevWBqf-1": "<h3>Jammed & Stuck Shutters</h3>",
        "text_ZjVPrYjV4ny7YV5h-1": "<p>We can perform unjam and stuck shutter repairs for most mechanical cameras.</p>",
        "text_3ubSAIis1Z8OAXms-1": "<h3>Door Replacement</h3>",
        "text_rgCiunvUGsyflbjz-1": "<p>We are able to replace the doors on many cameras, subject to parts availability.</p>",
        "text_GbMFJFCngCgXVmer-1": "<h3>Lens CLA</h3>",
        "text_IO0SzTfLrMc9Hmjy-1": "<p>We can CLA almost every detachable lens ever made and perform many lens specific repairs.</p>",
        "text_Rz7yyO07IB3auE3t-1": "<h3>Parts Replacement</h3>",
        "text_GFGnDjbsSg1sSZmu-1": "<p>We can replace many exterior parts, subject to availability.</p>",
        "text_UGmDsnOqjIyIyy3i-1": "<h3>Other Cameras</h3>",
        "text_K5rgZXTlX3nGlRJF-1": "<p>There is a vast array of other issues we can solve. If you're problem is not listed feel free to send us an email.</p>",
        "text_cQqIVEgqDtrrxC69-1": "<p>Transparent Pricing</p>",
        "text_tX5jvewh0rqW2AIv-1": "<p>Every camera is unique, so all repairs are quote-based after our bench inspection. Below are example price ranges to help you plan. Your actual quote may vary based on your camera's specific condition and required parts.</p>",
        "text_pjrwESGDUEHrdTL5-1": "<h3>$85–150</h3>",
        "text_faarjtbb0IW5JBxo-1": "<h4>Light Seals </h4>",
        "text_A7hnSbkawoWazFh9-1": "<h3>$150–250</h3>",
        "text_6HLaDCdaTccEYJs6-1": "<h4>Full Lens CLA</h4>",
        "text_jPpNrAJEvHro8fGY-1": "<h3>$325-850</h3>",
        "text_4tRf1aJI5bUz2mCE-1": "<h4>Camera CLA</h4>",
        "text_vdrhx0h7YdsU1RYN-1": "<h3>$90-150</h3>",
        "text_5SQU26miURpbtVBd-1": "<h4>Unjam</h4>",
        "url_vXX8izTIbPsVDqLd-1": "shopify://products/35mm-and-medium-format-repair",
        "text_ZSSb2jGJ33AH7IaV-1": "<p>See More</p>",
        "reviews_url": "",
        "review_1_body": "Sent in my AE-1 Program that had been sitting in a drawer for years. They diagnosed it quickly, sent a clear quote, and had it back shooting perfectly in under 3 weeks.",
        "review_1_name": "Marcus T.",
        "review_1_service": "Canon AE-1 Program CLA",
        "review_2_body": "Brought my Hasselblad in for a full CLA. Isabelle did incredible work. Communication throughout was excellent and the camera came back feeling brand new.",
        "review_2_name": "Priya L.",
        "review_2_service": "Hasselblad 500CM CLA",
        "review_3_body": "Mailed in a Contax T2 with a stuck shutter. Got a detailed quote within days, approved it, and had it back shooting within two weeks.",
        "review_3_name": "Daniel K.",
        "review_3_service": "Contax T2 Repair",
        "text_7aESZrg5i4gIDe2I-1": "<h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>",
        "text_9eTXhF2Jl59s8a6I-1": "<p>Everything you need to know about our camera repair service. Can't find your answer?</p>",
        "url_hkfu6CK8SSCaCMoo-1": "shopify://pages/visit",
        "text_suzeb1nmUompX5cX-1": "<p>Contact Us</p>",
        "text_yPOfQDQyudoffbEH-1": "<h4>What is the $50 bench fee and why is it non-refundable?</h4>",
        "text_DyX1AepcieaXngSX-1": "<p>The $50 bench fee is a non-refundable inspection charge that covers our technician's time to thoroughly assess your camera. This fee is applied toward your final repair cost if you proceed with the repair.</p>",
        "text_2uvk73piGaJVfSA1-1": "<h4>How long will my repair take?</h4>",
        "text_ENPmwIUdsO9w8ai3-1": "<p>Our estimated repair time is 2 – 4 weeks from the date we receive your camera. Complex repairs, special parts, and unforseen issues may create delays. We dcannot guarantee a specific time frame but will do our best to repair your camera ASAP.</p>",
        "text_m9G2IMZMMGgH3J3w-1": "<h4>What cameras do you service?</h4>",
        "text_1YqXpD4kvhmSlv9K-1": "<p>We specialize in 35mm and medium format film cameras including Canon, Nikon, Pentax, Olympus, Minolta, Contax, Leica, Hasselblad, Mamiya, Rolleiflex, Yashica, and so many more! If you're unsure whether we service your camera model, contact us before submitting a repair request.</p>",
        "text_JUKnHXd2MfaYQ4lL-1": "<h4>Do you repair Polaroid cameras?</h4>",
        "text_nKyOLcNCxQ9BU6Lx-1": "<p>Polaroid cameras require specialized service. Please visit our dedicated Polaroid Repairs page for information on instant camera repair options and pricing.</p>",
        "text_9SpfQZ8nomRE73wp-1": "<h4>How should I pack my camera for shipping?</h4>",
        "text_Ek5DbpeAU9rLi2mh-1": "<p>Wrap your camera in bubble wrap or foam padding and place it in a sturdy box with additional packing material to prevent movement. Remove batteries and any detachable lenses.</p>",
        "text_ReexIItutqMaLTuP-1": "<h4>Will I receive a quote before any work is done?</h4>",
        "text_U5chG9FSxzdJdnk9-1": "<p>Absolutely. After the bench inspection, we'll contact you with a detailed quote outlining all recommended repairs and costs. No repair work proceeds until you approve the estimate. You can decline the repair, though the bench fee is non-refundable.</p>",
        "text_YIEerFC852DhgYeL-1": "<h4>What payment methods do you accept?</h4>",
        "text_Xqgk9OZXuw21n0iY-1": "<p>We accept all major credit cards, PayPal, and Shop Pay. The bench fee is collected when you submit your repair request. The remaining balance is due when you receive your quote.</p>",
        "text_QNSMFgbyON2JQ9sv-1": "<h4>Can I drop off my camera in person?</h4>",
        "text_FAZaZxa8kpRb1gbS-1": "<p>Yes! Local customers can drop off and pick up cameras at our Brooklyn location. Please submit your repair request online before dropping off your camera.</p>",
        "text_B6eNUe5cX9LOchif-1": "<h3>Secure Shipping & Handling</h3>",
        "url_shipping_label": "",
        "text_shipping_label_btn": "<p>Purchase a Shipping Label</p>",
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 0
      }
    }
